window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The Games are drawing nearer. To ensure the prosperity of the new Earth, Dale must also ensure that the world itself is ready. </p> <p>As the races begin to come together, new conflicts and fellowships arise. Some meet in the name of peace and explanation, while others meet on the field of war. For the being that presides over all, how will Dale handle this?</p>"; 
